#define R(p,a,t) mix(a*dot(p,a),p,cos(t))+sin(t)*cross(p,a)
#define H(h) (cos((h)*6.3+vec3(0,23,21))*.5+.5)

void mainImage(out vec4 O, vec2 C)
{
    vec3 r=iResolution,c=vec3(0),
    d=normalize(vec3(C-.5*r.xy,r.y));
    float i=0.,s,e,g=0.,t=iTime;
	for(;i++<90.;){
        vec4 p=vec4(g*d,.07);
        p.z-=.5;
        p.xyz=R(p.xyz,normalize(H(t*.1)),t*.2);
        s=2.;
        for(int j=0;j++<6;)
            p=.02-abs(p-.1),
            s*=e=max(1./dot(p,p),1.3),
            p=abs(p.x<p.y?p.wzxy:p.wzyx)*e-1.3;
            g+=e=abs(length(p.xz*p.wy)-.02)/s+1e-4;
	    c+=mix(vec3(1),H(log(s)*.3),.4)*.04/exp(i*i*e);
	}
	c*=c*c;
    O=vec4(c,1);
}
